sequenceDiagram
participant A
participant B
participant C
loop Outer Work
    A->>+B: Start
    Note over A,B: Coordinate
    par Parallel Branches
        B->>+C: Ship
    and Fallback
        C-->>-B: Return
    end
    rect rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
        B->>C: Retry
        destroy C
        B--xC: Stop
    end
end
